<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <title>Under Construction — Nathan Rumsey</title>
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

      body {
        min-height: 100svh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: #0a0a0a;
        color: #e5e5e5;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 480px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .name {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #8a8a8a;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 2.25rem);
        font-weight: 600;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #a3a3a3;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      a {
        color: #e5e5e5;
        text-underline-offset: 3px;
      }

      a:hover {
        color: #ffffff;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="container">
      <p class="name">nathanrumsey.dev</p>
      <h1>Under Construction</h1>
      <p>Something new is on the way. Check back soon.</p>
      <p>
        In the meantime, reach me at
        <a href="mailto:nathan@nathanrumsey.dev">nathan@nathanrumsey.dev</a>
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
